This paper discusses the challenges and solutions related to networking and communication in IoT systems, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a novel architecture that integrates software defined networking (SDN) and data distribution service (DDS) middleware, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC), distributed systems (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of quality of service (QoS) support, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
